                           .   oooo         o8o
                         .o8   `888         `"'
  .ooooo.  oooo d8b    .o888oo  888 .oo.   oooo   .oooo.o
 d88' `88b `888""8P      888    888P"Y88b  `888  d88(  "8
 888   888  888          888    888   888   888  `"Y88b.
 888   888  888          888 .  888   888   888  o.  )88b
 `Y8bod8P' d888b         "888" o888o o888o o888o 8""888P'

