   or this:

      #           #              #             #
 ##########      #######    ##########    ##########
     #    #     #     #         #    #         #
     #    #    # #   #          #    #         #
    #     #       ###          #     #        #
   #   # #       ##           #   # #        #
  #     #      ##            #     #       ##

This contains the standard distribution fonts but more are available
from the homepage. Fonts should be untarred into /usr/share/figlet/
